  - TossWord now opens public screen named "TOSSWORD" in order to permit MUI
    settings window to be opened there.

  - Dictionary from now is being periodically validated (who can be 100% sure
    that concurrently running tasks in your Amiga are absolutely "bugs free"
    and even the Tossword itself has no bugs? Better safe, than sorry...)
